WEBVTT

1
00:04:28.810 --> 00:04:32.600 
都少不了我的一生知己  卡斯摩·布朗
would have to include my lifelong friend, Cosmo Brown.

2
00:04:32.810 --> 00:04:35.650 
我们一起长大一起工作
We were kids together, grew up together, worked together.

3
00:04:35.900 --> 00:04:36.820 
是吗
Yes?

4
00:04:37.650 --> 00:04:42.570 
杜拉  我有一个座右铭
Well, Dora, I've had one motto which I've always lived by:

5
00:04:43.200 --> 00:04:46.120 
尊严  尊严至上
"Dignity. Always dignity."

6
00:04:46.790 --> 00:04:50.960 
这是我爸妈  从小灌输给我的观念
This was instilled in me by Mum and Dad from the very beginning.

7
00:04:51.210 --> 00:04:54.460 
他们送我上一流的学校  包括舞蹈学校
They sent me to the finest schools, including dancing school.

8
00:04:54.670 --> 00:04:56.800 
在那里我初见卡斯摩
That's where I first met Cosmo.

9
00:04:57.050 --> 00:05:01.260 
我和他经常在我爸妈的朋友面前表演
And with him, I used to perform for Mum and Dad's society friends.

